he
added,
"Ah!
it
is
no
difficulty
to
see
who
you
take
after!
Your
dear
mother
was
so
clever
at
all
those
things!
If
I
had
but
her
memory!
But
I
can
remember
nothing;
not
even
that
particular
riddle
which
you
have
heard
me
mention;
I
can
only
recollect
the
first
