and
there
are
several.
Kitty,
a
fair
but
frozen
maid,
Kindled
a
flame
I
yet
deplore,
The
hood
wink'd
boy
I
called
to
aid,
Though
of
his
near
approach
afraid,
So
fatal
to
my
suit
before.
And
that
is
all
that
I
can
recollect
of
it
but
it
is
very
clever
all
